rules.ruleString: Incompatible with achievement in (I/W) {BTX5190, BTX9190, LAW7028, LAW7209}
Unit was previously coded {BTF9190%, BTX9190, FIN6190, FIN9190, TBF9190}

description: Topics include law of international trade, including rights and duties in international sales transactions; legal regimes governing contracts for carriage of goods internationally; distribution agreements; legal aspects of financing international trade; shipping documents, documentary collections and letters of credit; marine and aviation insurance; international dispute resolution.
